    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Business logic abuse vulnerability: Fraudsters can use the pipeline illustrated in <tt>image_a2badd.png</tt> to execute automated "card testing" attacks. We need to throttle and block rapid-fire, low-value authorization attempts hitting the <tt>Payment Processor</tt>.</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

