        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Security review of the data flow pipeline (<tt>Fintech API Gateway</tt> -&gt; <tt>Payment Processor</tt> -&gt; <tt>Transaction DB</tt> in <tt>image_a2badd.png</tt>) highlights a risk of injection attacks. If malicious strings bypass the gateway, they could directly compromise the database, leading to mass information disclosure of financial records.</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

