    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>To prevent parameter tampering of payment payloads in transit between the untrusted Customer zone and the internal <tt>Fintech API Gateway</tt> (refer to data flow in <tt>image_a2badd.png</tt>), we must enforce strict encryption and cryptographic integrity verification.</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

