    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Currently, the perimeter crossing into our trust boundary (as seen in <tt>image_a2badd.png</tt> where the Customer requests enter the <tt>Fintech API Gateway</tt>) lacks adequate protection against automated credential stuffing and request spoofing. Attackers can simulate legitimate customer requests to execute unauthorized actions.</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

